  "title": "*URGENT* CONTRACT DENTAL ASSISTANTS NEEDED! #HCGT",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>-         \nAssist\nthe Dental Surgeon / Dental Officer / Oral Health Therapist in General\nDentistry</p><p>-         \nComply\nwith work safety regulations and ensure cleanliness and sterility of dental\ninstruments and equipment</p><p>-         \nComply\nwith Infection Control practices and maintain Infection Control standards</p><p>-         \nEducate\npatients on dental and post-operative care</p><p>-         \nAssist\nwith patient charting and record-keeping</p><p>-         \nOther\nad-hoc duties</p><p>Job Requirement:</p><p>-         \nMinimum\nN/O/A Levels/NITEC in Dental Assisting</p><p>-         \nRelevant\nexperience is highly preferred but not a must</p><p>-         \nTeam\nplayer with strong communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>-         \nStrong\ntime management and organizational skills</p><p>-         \nIT\nsavvy</p><p>All qualified\napplicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)<br />\nRecruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No.\n199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>",
